videos.description: A.J. Hoggard comes off the screen and lobs it up to Marcus Bingham Jr. who gathers and flushes it in one jump.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hoggard goes up top to Bingham for the jam) 2022/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hoggard goes up top to Bingham for the jam

videos.description: Jaden Ivey lobs it up to where only Zach Edey can get it and he nearly tears down the rim on the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ivey lobs it up for Edey's slam) 2022/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ivey lobs it up for Edey's slam

videos.description: A great play design leads to Malik Hall lobbing it up to Julius Marble II for the two-handed jam.
